data.description: Welcome to your dream oasis featuring easy maintenance living!  This enchanting 3-bedroom, 2-full-bath hideaway invites you into a world where comfort meets style. Step inside to discover the magic of vaulted ceilings in the living room, creating an open and airy ambiance.  Wave goodbye to carpet! This unit features laminate wood flooring throughout for easy to clean floors! But wait, there's more! Venture out to your back deck and be spellbound by the serene beauty of a pool view that promises endless days of relaxation and fun under the sun. This isn't just a home, it's your personal retreat. So why wait? Dive into the life you've always wanted! Your enchanted living awaits!
